      "date": "2011-10-30 16:30:16.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/7031ff80-0311-11e1-bb4f-52540025f9af).  Ran 15 tests.  1 tests failed: replay-dual.",
